Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.67,0:23:22.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3a55\fad(500,500)}你那可愛的舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:27.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3a55\fad(500,500)}使我不經意臉紅起來
